+modal('jitera-context', "Context / Tribal Knowledge")
  p Designed and built the Context and Tribal Knowledge system — Jitera's solution for giving agents persistent, structured awareness of a user's projects, documents, and history.
  p The system supported semantic lookup, memory ingestion from multiple sources (documents, code, integrations), lineage tracking (so agents could explain where they learned something), and recall frequency tracking to surface the most relevant memories first.
  p The architecture balanced free-form associative retrieval with structured entity storage, making it practical for both developers and non-technical users.
